    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将负责钻井平台的各项运营，从资源的开采、设备的保养，到确保每位船员的安全。你的每一个选择都将直接影响结果——是独立解决突发状况，还是寻求团队的支持？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/43173ecdb4ccb9a505a1f4847586f248.poster.avif?t=1763888424\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/43173ecdb4ccb9a505a1f4847586f248.webm?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/43173ecdb4ccb9a505a1f4847586f248.mp4?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天，你都将面对新的考验：多变的气候、突如其来的设备问题，以及不可预知的紧急情况。通过第一人称的视角，你将深入体验海上钻井作业的点点滴滴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/3d71d87c639548e25ec502fc1d68d0fc.poster.avif?t=1763888424\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/3d71d87c639548e25ec502fc1d68d0fc.webm?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/3d71d87c639548e25ec502fc1d68d0fc.mp4?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩大你的钻井平台，升级你的设备，关怀你的船员，确保在波涛汹涌的大海中稳扎稳打。昼夜更替，真实模拟的天气系统，让每一个决策都显得至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/cc12c73cf00ace68e2793d0528ddab8a.poster.avif?t=1763888424\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/cc12c73cf00ace68e2793d0528ddab8a.webm?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/cc12c73cf00ace68e2793d0528ddab8a.mp4?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用各式工具和技术，解决层出不穷的问题——无论是简单的修理，还是复杂的救援任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/146d297a479f37695ff397ea722673ce.poster.avif?t=1763888424\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/146d297a479f37695ff397ea722673ce.webm?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/146d297a479f37695ff397ea722673ce.mp4?t=1763888424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >石油リグでの生活に向かう覚悟は出来てますか？この仕事がもたらす困難を乗り越えられることを証明して下さい。外洋上でどんな物語を織り成すかは貴方次第なのです。</p>",
